es/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解要幾個平底鑊?"},{"pid":"7e0250a4a165c4f6f377172da2dcdd83bb17fe8c","tid":46300,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:03:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實牛排衣家野，同海鮮一樣，靚既唔洗搞甘多調味，鹽同黑白椒就ok，最多加D Rosemary番茜，甚至係超市買支Season $4X~6X一支就搞掂，只有肉質差既先要搞花臣，所以甘樣不如慳D錢去Citysuper或者其他出口店買勁靚牛排返屋企整仲好啦</blockquote><br />\n衣你老母個臭閪<br />\n甘你老母個臭閪</blockquote><br />\n好撚醒喎"},{"pid":"99bb9dedfb0de287f950bceacdb63905625b6557","tid":46300,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:13:34.000Z","msg":"新鮮靚既話食5成或以下，調完味大火封面，再中火煎一煎有色就食生生地咁"},{"pid":"b259da8ec15b0d25a1c9d99c56896f15ba8c0bdd","tid":46300,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:16:22.000Z","msg":"如果要食7或全熟好難煮煎得好食，通常煎面再焗，唔係好難平均熟"},{"pid":"0aa29d93a953527a742e1e459d7fd669ab665b93","tid":46300,"uid":17744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:18:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗撚咁煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n燒紅個pan，大火每邊煎80-90秒，叮多30-45秒<br />\n搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同你搞一大輪慢慢煎一撚樣，不過好多保守黨都對微波有偏見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n焗爐會唔會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f957b0805702eea4fc7514ab547de72a9367cc60","tid":46300,"uid":63661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:33:57.000Z","msg":"舊牛靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e20ea72af0f15b6dd2c8df524401b29ea4e7c0","tid":46300,"uid":8632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:44:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我以前就同上面一樣煮法<br />\n<br />\n但其實唔太健康<br />\n<br />\n1. 如用易結鑊大火係會好多毒物<br />\n<br />\n2. 如啲油去到出煙，都會好多致癌物<br />\n<br />\n3. 用olive oil 你唔用pomace，個smoke point勁低，唔太健康<br />\n<br />\n利申：呢家