br />\n用力壓姆指下面果舊肉<br />\n呢個就係五成熟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實用手feel呢下好考經驗，初手最實際買支溫度針，最平十蚊有交易，先封晒四邊，再煎到咁上下督入牛扒中心，用左温度針好少失手overcook<br />\n大約55-60度3成<br />\n大約60-65度5成<br />\n大約65-75度7成<br />\n高過77度就柴皮<br />\n煎完最緊要放5-10分鐘比塊牛扒rest"},{"pid":"1f17c754645ea7846acb7adac36dee59a5253e22","tid":46300,"uid":33837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc"},{"pid":"3561f466fe65f98eb97227382dce61c87d03d7b6","tid":46300,"uid":62393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:16:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實牛排衣家野，同海鮮一樣，靚既唔洗搞甘多調味，鹽同黑白椒就ok，最多加D Rosemary番茜，甚至係超市買支Season $4X~6X一支就搞掂，只有肉質差既先要搞花臣，所以甘樣不如慳D錢去Citysuper或者其他出口店買勁靚牛排返屋企整仲好啦</blockquote><br />\n衣你老母個臭閪<br />\n甘你老母個臭閪</blockquote><br />\n引用唔哂兩個新會員<br />\nwelcome to lihkg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人屌你又屌<br />\n唔識規矩又衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405e9a4d425f2b18ffac311e5c49b557d8180972","tid":46300,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:17:04.000Z","msg":"1分鐘一面 大火 反45秒 <br />\n出血水 6成 再等20秒 搞掂"},{"pid":"2a4ca637407aa58f7b51b734068ae42b6f437ae6","tid":46300,"uid":36359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:29:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我以前就同上面一樣煮法<br />\n<br />\n但其實唔太健康<br />\n<br />\n1. 如用易結鑊大火係會好多毒物<br />\n<br />\n2. 如啲油去到出煙，都會好多致癌物<br />\n<br />\n3. 用olive oil 你唔用pomace，個smoke point勁低，唔太健康<br />\n<br />\n利申：呢家研究用鑄鐵鍋煎又或者sous vide再煎/火槍</blockquote><br />\n邊有人用易潔鑊煎牛扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一開頭成件事已經錯哂"},{"pid":"a54d1fbc152b7c4f7a1fa6f8c60d00c606ed5bb5","tid":46300,"uid":343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:30:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實牛排衣